data.description: This charming home sits on nearly 2 acres of wooded privacy w/ a creek running through the corner of the property! Peaceful serenity! Split bedroom plan, master on main and high ceilings in the living room with a stone fireplace. Spacious kitchen and separate dining room! Upstairs is a perfect teen suite w/ full bathroom. The daylight basement is partially finished w/ boat door and its own driveway for easy access! Close to 441 and I-85.
